<plot>James is a mousy man who tells his therapist that, "since that day," he's been able to do special things. He puts on a pair of aviator sunglasses and boldly announces, as if talking to his wife, that he's a superhero. During the rest of his day, he helps an old lady across the street and returns a lost dog. Once home, however, his wife is hardly sympathetic that he's late and hasn't found a job. He puts on the sunglasses and makes his announcement. Will she be impressed?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?032929</url></doc>
